Enum Documentation¶

enum BIQUAD_FILTER_ORDER¶

: Biquad filter order. The higher the order, the more intense the filtering effect

Values:

BIQUAD_ORDER_2 = 1¶

2nd order

BIQUAD_ORDER_4 = 2¶

4th order

BIQUAD_ORDER_6 = 3¶

6th order

BIQUAD_ORDER_8 = 4¶

8th order
